gov.nih.nlm.meme.sql
Interface DataSourceConstants

All Superinterfaces:
MEMEConstants
All Known Subinterfaces:
DataSourceConstants, ServerConstants, ServerConstants
public interface DataSourceConstants
extends MEMEConstants

This interface holds constants commonly used by the MEME data source APIs. It supplements the MEMEConstants. Most of the constants represent property names.

Author:
MEME Group
See Also:
MEMEConstants
